aby for 2017! Please vote here daily! Congestive Heart Failure Clinic now open in Erath (March 7, 2017)  -- Abbeville General has opened a Congestive Heart Failure Clinic on Tuesdays in the Erath/Delcambre Community Care Clinic.  Lauren Ledoux, APRN-FNP-C, is the provider in the clinic. Dr. Maria Fontanez joins the Abbeville General Team! (March 6, 2017)  -- Abbeville General welcomes Dr. Maria Fontanez, Pediatrician, to our Pediatric Clinic, (formerly the Manuel Medical Clinic) located across from the Emergency Department. Erath/Delcambre Community Care Clinic now open 7-5 Monday-Friday (November 14, 2016) -- The Erath /Delcambre Community Care Clinic is now open 7:00-5:00 Monday-Friday which includes the lunch hour. Abbeville General Report to Rotary Club (November 13, 2016) -- Ray Landry,
